<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>좌석 선택</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <!-- 예매창 전용 CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/booking-seat.css">
</head>

<body>
<main class="cc-main">
    <div class="cc-container">

        <header class="cc-popup-header">
            <div>
                <div class="cc-popup-header__title">🎫 좌석 선택</div>
                <div class="cc-popup-header__meta">좌석 선택 후 10분 이내에 결제를 진행해주세요.</div>
            </div>
            <button type="button" class="cc-popup-close" onclick="window.close()">창 닫기</button>
        </header>

        <div class="cc-stepper" aria-label="예매 진행 단계">
            <div class="cc-step is-done"><span class="cc-step__num">✓</span>예매정보</div>
            <span class="cc-step-line"></span>
            <div class="cc-step is-active"><span class="cc-step__num">2</span>좌석선택</div>
            <span class="cc-step-line"></span>
            <div class="cc-step"><span class="cc-step__num">3</span>결제</div>
            <span class="cc-step-line"></span>
            <div class="cc-step"><span class="cc-step__num">4</span>완료</div>
        </div>

        <section class="cc-seat-layout">

            <!-- 왼쪽 공연 요약 -->
            <aside>
                <div class="cc-card cc-booking-summary">
                    <div class="cc-booking-summary__dark">
                        <span class="cc-badge cc-badge--fill">단독판매</span>

                        <h2>
                            {{#concert.title}}{{concert.title}}{{/concert.title}}
                            {{^concert.title}}테스트 콘서트{{/concert.title}}
                        </h2>

                        <p class="cc-booking-summary__line">
                            📅
                            {{#sessionText}}{{sessionText}}{{/sessionText}}
                            {{^sessionText}}2026.06.27 (토) 18:00{{/sessionText}}
                        </p>

                        <p class="cc-booking-summary__line">
                            📍
                            {{#venueText}}{{venueText}}{{/venueText}}
                            {{^venueText}}서울 · 올림픽공원 올림픽홀{{/venueText}}
                        </p>

                        <div class="cc-booking-summary__poster">
                            <img
                                    src="{{#concert.posterUrl}}{{concert.posterUrl}}{{/concert.posterUrl}}{{^concert.posterUrl}}/images/sample/poster-legend-seoul.svg{{/concert.posterUrl}}"
                                    alt="공연 포스터">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="cc-card cc-booking-info">
                    <h3>예매 정보</h3>

                    <div class="cc-mini-row">
                        <b>관람일시</b>
                        <span>
                            {{#sessionText}}{{sessionText}}{{/sessionText}}
                            {{^sessionText}}2026.06.27 (토) 18:00{{/sessionText}}
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="cc-mini-row">
                        <b>관람장소</b>
                        <span>
                            {{#venueName}}{{venueName}}{{/venueName}}
                            {{^venueName}}올림픽공원 올림픽홀{{/venueName}}
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="cc-mini-row"><b>관람등급</b><span>만 7세 이상</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-mini-row"><b>관람시간</b><span>120분</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-mini-row"><b>매수제한</b><span>회차당 1인 4매</span></div>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <!-- 중앙 좌석 선택 -->
            <section class="cc-card cc-seat-map-card">
                <div class="cc-seat-redesign">

                    <!-- 왼쪽: 전체 좌석도 -->
                    <aside class="cc-zone-overview">
                        <div class="cc-zone-overview__head">
                            <strong>전체 좌석도</strong>
                            <span>좌석 등급을 선택하세요</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="cc-zone-overview__image-box">
                            <img src="/images/sample/seat.jpg" alt="전체 좌석도" class="cc-zone-overview__image">
                        </div>

                        <div class="cc-zone-tabs" aria-label="좌석 등급 선택">
                            {{#seat.gradeTabs}}
                                <button type="button"
                                        class="cc-zone-tab {{#active}}is-active{{/active}}"
                                        data-grade="{{grade}}">
                                    {{gradeName}}
                                </button>
                            {{/seat.gradeTabs}}

                            {{^seat.gradeTabs}}
                                <button type="button" class="cc-zone-tab is-active" data-grade="">좌석 없음</button>
                            {{/seat.gradeTabs}}
                        </div>

                        <div class="cc-zone-legend">
                            <div><i class="cc-seat-sample cc-seat-sample--available"></i>예매 가능</div>
                            <div><i class="cc-seat-sample cc-seat-sample--selected"></i>선택 좌석</div>
                            <div><i class="cc-seat-sample cc-seat-sample--sold"></i>매진</div>
                        </div>
                    </aside>

                    <!-- 오른쪽: 선택 등급 좌석 -->
                    <section class="cc-zone-detail">
                        <div class="cc-zone-detail__top">
                            <div>
                                <h3 id="zoneTitle">좌석 등급</h3>
                                <p id="zoneSubText">DB에 등록된 좌석을 표시합니다.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cc-zone-stage">STAGE</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="cc-zone-guide">
                            좌석 번호를 클릭하면 오른쪽 선택 좌석에 추가됩니다. 최대 4석까지 선택할 수 있습니다.
                        </div>

                        <div id="zoneSeatGrid" class="cc-zone-seat-grid" aria-label="좌석 선택"></div>

                        <div class="cc-zone-bottom">
                            <button type="button" class="cc-small-btn" id="resetZoneBtn">좌석 다시 선택</button>
                            <span id="seatHoverInfo">좌석에 마우스를 올리면 좌석 정보가 표시됩니다.</span>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 오른쪽 선택 좌석 -->
            <aside>
                <div class="cc-card cc-selected-card">
                    <h3>선택 좌석</h3>

                    <div class="cc-timer">
                        <span>좌석 보관 시간</span>
                        <b data-countdown="600">10:00</b>
                    </div>

                    <h4>선택 내역</h4>

                    <div class="cc-selected-list">
                        <div class="cc-selected-seat">
                            <div>
                                <div class="cc-selected-seat__name">선택된 좌석이 없습니다.</div>
                                <div class="cc-selected-seat__price">좌석을 선택하면 여기에 표시됩니다.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="cc-total">
                        <span>총 0석</span>
                        <strong class="cc-total__price">0원</strong>
                    </div>

                    <form action="/booking/payment" method="post" class="cc-payment-form">
                        {{#_csrf}}
                            <input type="hidden" name="{{parameterName}}" value="{{token}}">
                        {{/_csrf}}

                        <input type="hidden" name="concertId"
                               value="{{#concert.id}}{{concert.id}}{{/concert.id}}{{^concert.id}}{{concertId}}{{/concert.id}}">

                        <input type="hidden" name="sessionId"
                               value="{{#sessionId}}{{sessionId}}{{/sessionId}}{{^sessionId}}1{{/sessionId}}">

                        <input type="hidden" name="seatIds" id="selectedSeatIds">

                        <button class="cc-btn cc-btn--primary cc-btn--full" type="submit">다음 단계</button>
                    </form>

                    <a class="cc-btn cc-btn--outline cc-btn--full cc-prev-link"
                       href="/concerts/{{#concert.id}}{{concert.id}}{{/concert.id}}{{^concert.id}}{{concertId}}{{/concert.id}}">
                        이전 단계
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="cc-card cc-notice-card">
                    <h3>유의사항</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>좌석 보관 시간이 초과되면 선택 좌석이 자동으로 해제됩니다.</li>
                        <li>무통장 입금 선택 시 예매 당일 23:59까지 입금해야 예매가 완료됩니다.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </aside>

        </section>
    </div>
</main>

<script>
    window.CATCHCATCH_SEATS = {{{seat.seatsJson}}};
</script>
<script src="/js/booking-seat.js"></script>
</body>
</html>